1
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:24,420
♪It's a sordid story that you've made♪

2
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:32,700
♪Up to fill my mind with doubts and pain♪

3
00:00:34,780 --> 00:00:40,220
♪Blood I shed, and tears I wept,
are you satisfied?♪

4
00:00:40,220 --> 00:00:42,540
♪Enjoying what's mine♪

5
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:49,500
♪Have you found a way
to bury guilt and shame♪

6
00:00:50,540 --> 00:00:55,020
♪I'm coming back to life♪

7
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Through the seven gates of death♪

8
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:02,820
♪I'm coming back survived♪

9
00:01:02,820 --> 00:01:06,580
♪Feeling great to see you fall♪

10
00:01:06,580 --> 00:01:10,820
♪I'm taking back what's mine♪

11
00:01:10,820 --> 00:01:15,340
♪Bringing horror to the battlefield♪

12
00:01:15,340 --> 00:01:19,060
♪Lay it to waste♪

13
00:01:19,060 --> 00:01:22,940
♪Til the day my kingdom is reclaimed♪

14
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:42,540
=Her Blaze=

15
00:01:43,260 --> 00:01:46,000
=Episode 27=

16
00:02:11,020 --> 00:02:12,240
(Take photo stickers)

17
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:13,599
I'd rather not.

18
00:02:15,180 --> 00:02:16,240
Take a photo as a memento.

19
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,879
Look, she wants to.

20
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:20,240
That sounds so ominous.

21
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:20,960
A memento...

22
00:02:22,759 --> 00:02:23,759
Come on, take one.

23
00:02:23,759 --> 00:02:24,520
Take it.

24
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:44,919
It looks better than I imagined.

25
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:49,120
You must smile more.

26
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:53,580
In this world, there are many things
worth being happy about.

27
00:02:56,759 --> 00:02:57,879
In this world,

28
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:00,759
bad people carry guns

29
00:03:00,759 --> 00:03:02,120
and snatch candy everywhere.

30
00:03:02,919 --> 00:03:03,800
As for the good people,

31
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:06,639
they are treated like candy

32
00:03:07,719 --> 00:03:09,800
by so-called rules, dignity, and honor,

33
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:13,719
and hidden away

34
00:03:14,159 --> 00:03:15,159
until they rot.

35
00:03:16,759 --> 00:03:17,719
Since that's the case,

36
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:20,039
I will go into the darkness.

37
00:03:21,319 --> 00:03:22,800
I'll figure out their rules

38
00:03:23,700 --> 00:03:25,039
and go all the way in my own way.

39
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:30,759
(Chen Mo,)

40
00:03:32,080 --> 00:03:32,840
(what I can't)

41
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:33,960
(tell you right now)

42
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:37,120
(is that returning to Lysen
is the most important step)

43
00:03:37,599 --> 00:03:38,840
(in my entire plan.)

44
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:41,120
(My ultimate goal)

45
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,879
(is to make the wicked pay.)

46
00:03:44,599 --> 00:03:47,319
(I want Jiang Dongchao
to fall from his high position at Lysen)

47
00:03:48,439 --> 00:03:50,110
(and receive
the punishment he deserves.)

48
00:04:04,719 --> 00:04:05,520
Sir Yang,

49
00:04:05,919 --> 00:04:07,080
I asked to meet you

50
00:04:07,319 --> 00:04:08,919
because I sincerely want to remind you.

51
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:11,199
The tripartite cooperation for financing

52
00:04:11,199 --> 00:04:12,919
will indeed help Bosi's transformation.

53
00:04:13,719 --> 00:04:15,159
But have you ever thought

54
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:18,000
that what if this financing

55
00:04:18,079 --> 00:04:19,199
is just to fulfill

56
00:04:19,199 --> 00:04:20,839
Jiang Dongchao's own agenda?

57
00:04:22,199 --> 00:04:23,160
Where's the evidence?

58
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:26,800
Jiang Dongchao acts cautiously.

59
00:04:27,199 --> 00:04:27,920
I don't have

60
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:28,959
definite evidence yet.

61
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:30,720
But

62
00:04:32,079 --> 00:04:33,079
I have calculated

63
00:04:33,079 --> 00:04:34,199
(Jiang Dongchao's Overseas Investment)
returns for all overseas investments

64
00:04:34,199 --> 00:04:35,639
(Jiang Dongchao's Overseas Investment)
and acquisition projects

65
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:37,360
(Jiang Dongchao's Overseas Investment)
since he joined Lysen.

66
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:41,900
(Reasons: bankruptcy, significant decline, failed business,
disappearance of major clients, asset loss, owner absconded)

67
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:44,439
Most of the investments

68
00:04:44,759 --> 00:04:45,920
had no follow-up.

69
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:49,279
I suspect he used the projects
to line his own pockets.

70
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:51,839
And it is likely

71
00:04:51,839 --> 00:04:53,800
that after your tripartite
financing conference,

72
00:04:53,959 --> 00:04:55,660
Jiang Dongchao
will repeat the same trick

73
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:57,519
and transfer the assets.

74
00:05:06,079 --> 00:05:08,480
There is one more important factor
you can't ignore.

75
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:11,160
Ms. Xin,

76
00:05:12,439 --> 00:05:14,000
I remember you told me

77
00:05:14,879 --> 00:05:16,480
that we were never enemies.

78
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:21,040
Pengyu.

79
00:05:23,439 --> 00:05:24,399
Hello, Little Genius.

80
00:05:25,519 --> 00:05:26,319
Miss Rao,

81
00:05:26,959 --> 00:05:29,079
psychological warfare isn't enough

82
00:05:30,100 --> 00:05:31,879
to deal with
Jiang Dongchao and Bai Qingyu.

83
00:05:32,079 --> 00:05:33,079
We have to produce

84
00:05:33,079 --> 00:05:34,160
something solid.

85
00:05:35,279 --> 00:05:36,920
Jiang Dongchao loathes me,

86
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:39,279
and he knows that I hold shares of Bosi.

87
00:05:39,279 --> 00:05:40,959
I don't believe that if I get involved,

88
00:05:42,100 --> 00:05:44,120
I still won't be able
to get the truth out of him.

89
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:48,160
They are trying hard to convince you

90
00:05:48,160 --> 00:05:50,120
to attend the financing conference
just to use

91
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,160
your company's endorsement

92
00:05:51,170 --> 00:05:52,960
to tell a good story
to the capital market,

93
00:05:52,970 --> 00:05:55,040
to trick more
shareholders into investing.

94
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:05,160
So,

95
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,240
you want me

96
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:08,680
to pretend to cooperate with them

97
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:11,079
and find a way to get evidence

98
00:06:11,079 --> 00:06:12,560
of their fund transfers?

99
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:16,040
On what grounds?

100
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:21,439
On the grounds that this matter
won't cause you any loss.

101
00:06:22,439 --> 00:06:23,680
If you don't believe me,

102
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:24,959
you can try.

103
00:06:25,199 --> 00:06:26,439
If what I said is wrong,

104
00:06:26,750 --> 00:06:28,680
you can sign the contract
with them at any time.

105
00:06:47,279 --> 00:06:48,079
Please.

106
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,720
I think you are very clear

107
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:08,759
about my purpose.

108
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:11,879
I invited Mr. Pengyu here

109
00:07:12,199 --> 00:07:13,959
just to express our sincerity.

110
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:20,120
Xian Pengyu
and Jiang Dongchao have a grudge.

111
00:07:20,839 --> 00:07:21,959
I can understand that.

112
00:07:23,439 --> 00:07:25,480
But what is your reason, Miss Rao?

113
00:07:25,879 --> 00:07:27,000
Back then, Jiang Dongchao

114
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:29,519
embezzled the project restart funds

115
00:07:29,519 --> 00:07:31,439
that I got from Mr. Li.

116
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:33,519
To reopen the Snack Street,

117
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:36,120
I traded a 4 percent stake in Bosi

118
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:37,839
with Mr. Pengyu.

119
00:07:39,519 --> 00:07:41,040
Jiang Dongchao held a grudge.

120
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:44,240
He teamed up with Bai Qingyu
and Bai Liangliang

121
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:48,160
to beat me like this.

122
00:07:52,519 --> 00:07:53,879
So, what do you think my reason is?

123
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:00,959
Mr. Yang,

124
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:03,079
my goal is very simple.

125
00:08:03,700 --> 00:08:04,800
I want to avenge my father.

126
00:08:06,279 --> 00:08:07,839
As long as we join forces,

127
00:08:08,199 --> 00:08:10,120
plus the 4 percent stake
Little Genius holds,

128
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:11,519
Jiang Dongchao and Bai Qingyu

129
00:08:11,519 --> 00:08:13,279
won't stand a chance.

130
00:08:13,959 --> 00:08:15,560
Name any condition you want,

131
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:16,720
and I will agree.

132
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:19,759
Because I want to take down
Jiang Dongchao at any cost.

133
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,720
So now you know to beg me.

134
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:37,080
That wasn't your attitude before.

135
00:08:46,519 --> 00:08:47,320
In the past,

136
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:50,639
I was immature

137
00:08:51,559 --> 00:08:52,720
and reckless.

138
00:08:55,519 --> 00:08:56,360
From now on,

139
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:58,000
I

140
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:00,799
will respect your thoughts and opinions.

141
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:02,799
I'll put you first in everything.

142
00:09:03,519 --> 00:09:04,320
And right here,

143
00:09:04,759 --> 00:09:05,559
I

144
00:09:06,919 --> 00:09:08,320
sincerely apologize to you.

145
00:09:11,879 --> 00:09:12,840
Please forgive me,

146
00:09:14,399 --> 00:09:15,200
Sir.

147
00:09:22,519 --> 00:09:25,279
Since you've put it that way,

148
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:29,200
I have no reason

149
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,080
not to agree.

150
00:09:37,799 --> 00:09:38,879
Thank you, Mr. Yang.

151
00:09:41,159 --> 00:09:42,320
Then, it's a deal.

152
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:44,080
It's a deal.

153
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:17,919
You all heard it.

154
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:23,039
This is the sincerity I'm showing you.

155
00:10:24,320 --> 00:10:25,120
You said

156
00:10:26,279 --> 00:10:28,559
you could help me take Bosi private.

157
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,600
How will you do it?

158
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:33,360
I've already shown my hand.

159
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:35,039
If I don't see

160
00:10:35,039 --> 00:10:36,159
your sincerity today,

161
00:10:38,039 --> 00:10:39,240
don't blame me

162
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:41,519
for choosing to work with them.

163
00:10:41,519 --> 00:10:42,320
Sir,

164
00:10:44,039 --> 00:10:45,200
don't be in a hurry.

165
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:47,639
Dongchao already has a plan.

166
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:48,639
Sir,

167
00:10:49,759 --> 00:10:51,480
although our goals are different,

168
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:55,279
all of this

169
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:57,990
must be achieved through
a tripartite cooperation

170
00:10:59,639 --> 00:11:00,799
and financing.

171
00:11:04,679 --> 00:11:05,480
Rest assured,

172
00:11:08,080 --> 00:11:08,879
helping you

173
00:11:11,639 --> 00:11:12,679
is helping myself.

174
00:11:21,039 --> 00:11:21,840
By the way,

175
00:11:23,759 --> 00:11:25,559
Sir, Ms. Bai,

176
00:11:26,639 --> 00:11:28,120
please turn off your phones.

177
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:31,279
Turn off.

178
00:11:31,799 --> 00:11:32,600
Turn them off.

179
00:11:33,380 --> 00:11:35,120
(Power off)

180
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:36,440
Please forgive my caution.

181
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:39,000
Mine is off.

182
00:11:43,300 --> 00:11:44,860
(Power off)

183
00:11:51,519 --> 00:11:52,720
I will use part of the funds

184
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:55,159
raised at this financing conference
to acquire

185
00:11:55,879 --> 00:11:57,159
overseas tech companies.

186
00:11:57,440 --> 00:11:59,240
That way, I can legitimately

187
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:01,000
move this money abroad.

188
00:12:01,159 --> 00:12:02,519
(I calculated the returns on all)

189
00:12:02,639 --> 00:12:04,080
(of Jiang Dongchao's overseas)

190
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:05,799
(investments and acquisitions.)

191
00:12:05,919 --> 00:12:07,080
(Most of the investments)

192
00:12:07,480 --> 00:12:08,600
(never went anywhere.)

193
00:12:10,639 --> 00:12:11,519
The money will go

194
00:12:11,519 --> 00:12:12,879
to my BVI company accounts.

195
00:12:13,039 --> 00:12:15,440
It's a dedicated platform,
safe and hidden.

196
00:12:15,759 --> 00:12:17,480
I'll split this money into

197
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:20,639
three parts

198
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:21,519
and transfer them

199
00:12:21,519 --> 00:12:23,679
to three offshore trusts.

200
00:12:27,639 --> 00:12:28,879
We'll take it step by step.

201
00:12:29,159 --> 00:12:30,679
Li Wancheng will never know.

202
00:12:31,279 --> 00:12:32,840
Sir, you can use this method

203
00:12:32,919 --> 00:12:33,840
to put Bosi's money

204
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:35,000
into your own pocket

205
00:12:35,679 --> 00:12:37,720
and take Bosi private.

206
00:12:39,919 --> 00:12:40,720
And Ms. Bai,

207
00:12:41,759 --> 00:12:42,480
you can also take

208
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:43,960
this clean money,

209
00:12:44,279 --> 00:12:46,919
retire with honor,
and enjoy your golden years.

210
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:53,279
As for me,

211
00:12:55,639 --> 00:12:56,600
I will lead Lysen

212
00:12:57,399 --> 00:12:58,320
and keep moving forward.

213
00:13:02,919 --> 00:13:03,720
Sir,

214
00:13:04,360 --> 00:13:06,240
Bosi's money will be taken out

215
00:13:07,279 --> 00:13:09,279
and put into your own pocket.

216
00:13:09,919 --> 00:13:11,159
It means you will still get

217
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:14,279
Bosi back, right?

218
00:13:14,279 --> 00:13:16,559
Since you say this money

219
00:13:16,720 --> 00:13:17,960
is what you earned

220
00:13:17,960 --> 00:13:19,039
with your own hard work,

221
00:13:19,919 --> 00:13:21,039
once you have it back,

222
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:22,480
you can make investments

223
00:13:22,720 --> 00:13:24,960
or continue with your industries.

224
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:28,759
That's up to you, right?

225
00:13:33,260 --> 00:13:34,740
(Xinkang Treatment Center)

226
00:13:40,519 --> 00:13:41,320
Are you

227
00:13:42,559 --> 00:13:43,639
happy here?

228
00:13:43,639 --> 00:13:44,399
Yes.

229
00:13:44,879 --> 00:13:45,679
That's good.

230
00:13:49,799 --> 00:13:51,200
I never knew

231
00:13:52,639 --> 00:13:53,679
that the 4 percent

232
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:56,279
in Rao Yuci's hands was given by you.

233
00:13:56,279 --> 00:13:57,279
Of course.

234
00:13:57,840 --> 00:13:59,960
I treat her like my own daughter.

235
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:02,240
This daughter of yours

236
00:14:02,679 --> 00:14:05,159
is quite remarkable.

237
00:14:05,519 --> 00:14:06,320
For Lysen

238
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:08,480
to turn the current situation around,

239
00:14:08,759 --> 00:14:09,559
I think

240
00:14:10,000 --> 00:14:11,679
it won't work without her.

241
00:14:12,120 --> 00:14:13,519
You must protect her well

242
00:14:13,759 --> 00:14:15,440
and don't let her get hurt again.

243
00:14:21,159 --> 00:14:22,000
Xian Pengyu and I

244
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:23,559
have already met Yang Jinwan.

245
00:14:24,159 --> 00:14:26,750
Regarding the tripartite cooperation
proposed by Jiang Dongchao,

246
00:14:26,840 --> 00:14:28,360
he also has many doubts.

247
00:14:29,200 --> 00:14:31,200
Well, we will take this opportunity

248
00:14:31,480 --> 00:14:33,519
to let Yang Jinwan join in and obtain

249
00:14:33,519 --> 00:14:35,080
evidence of Jiang Dongchao's crimes.

250
00:14:37,639 --> 00:14:38,480
Yang Jinwan

251
00:14:39,440 --> 00:14:40,840
might be a breakthrough.

252
00:14:41,639 --> 00:14:42,440
But

253
00:14:43,720 --> 00:14:44,720
are you confident?

254
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:46,919
Go with the flow.

255
00:14:48,039 --> 00:14:49,000
I'm clear

256
00:14:49,759 --> 00:14:50,879
that it's impossible

257
00:14:51,879 --> 00:14:52,639
for Jiang Dongchao

258
00:14:52,639 --> 00:14:54,000
to have any trust in me again.

259
00:14:54,919 --> 00:14:56,480
But now, there is a turning point.

260
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:57,879
Yang Jinwan

261
00:14:58,960 --> 00:15:00,960
has already sold me out
to Jiang Dongchao.

262
00:15:05,320 --> 00:15:08,320
The less Jiang Dongchao trusts you,

263
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:12,240
the more he will trust Yang Jinwan.

264
00:15:20,940 --> 00:15:22,700
(Consultation Center)

265
00:15:24,039 --> 00:15:25,559
Yuci, something big has happened!

266
00:15:25,639 --> 00:15:26,639
What exactly is going on?

267
00:15:27,360 --> 00:15:28,720
We have already checked.

268
00:15:28,730 --> 00:15:30,759
The Master already had
hypertension and geriatric diseases,

269
00:15:30,759 --> 00:15:32,440
coupled with a huge shock,

270
00:15:32,879 --> 00:15:35,000
so it triggered
an acute cerebral infarction.

271
00:15:35,559 --> 00:15:37,080
He has been resuscitated,

272
00:15:37,080 --> 00:15:38,720
but he probably won't

273
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:39,799
wake up for a while.

274
00:15:40,440 --> 00:15:42,200
He was fine, so how could he be shocked?

275
00:15:48,340 --> 00:15:50,540
(Jiang Dongchao)

276
00:15:51,600 --> 00:15:52,399
Yuci,

277
00:15:53,960 --> 00:15:55,240
let's meet.

278
00:16:21,799 --> 00:16:23,120
Yuci, you're here.

279
00:16:31,720 --> 00:16:34,759
(Nuan, go find Mom and Dad.)

280
00:16:35,919 --> 00:16:38,039
(Thank you. Goodbye.)

281
00:16:49,840 --> 00:16:51,200
This place is quite nice.

282
00:16:51,720 --> 00:16:53,039
It has the lively vibe you like.

283
00:16:57,679 --> 00:17:00,279
Yuci, today,

284
00:17:01,759 --> 00:17:03,399
let's have an open and honest talk.

285
00:17:04,440 --> 00:17:05,519
Sure, Mr. Jiang.

286
00:17:11,519 --> 00:17:12,319
Actually,

287
00:17:13,240 --> 00:17:14,759
you don't care about them

288
00:17:14,759 --> 00:17:15,720
as much as you say.

289
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:21,039
You aren't so naive

290
00:17:22,119 --> 00:17:24,920
to think that I don't know
what you're doing, right?

291
00:18:01,440 --> 00:18:03,599
Did Xin Shaonan agree to help you?

292
00:18:07,119 --> 00:18:07,920
Rao Yuci,

293
00:18:09,799 --> 00:18:12,960
the essence of human relationships
in our world

294
00:18:14,079 --> 00:18:14,960
is exchange.

295
00:18:15,519 --> 00:18:17,000
What you can give to others

296
00:18:17,680 --> 00:18:19,279
is what others will give back to you.

297
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:21,640
And if you have nothing

298
00:18:21,640 --> 00:18:22,519
and only talk about

299
00:18:22,519 --> 00:18:23,680
ideals and morality,

300
00:18:24,920 --> 00:18:26,559
ultimately, you will get nothing.

301
00:18:29,000 --> 00:18:30,720
Not everyone is like you.

302
00:18:31,480 --> 00:18:32,279
Is that so?

303
00:18:32,960 --> 00:18:33,759
Who is it?

304
00:18:35,640 --> 00:18:36,640
Is it Yang Jinwan?

305
00:18:38,160 --> 00:18:39,920
Right. I forgot to tell you,

306
00:18:40,359 --> 00:18:41,920
we reached a partnership long ago.

307
00:19:07,720 --> 00:19:08,680
You heard it all.

308
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:11,920
Who else is there?

309
00:19:18,480 --> 00:19:21,079
Your so-called Master, right?

310
00:20:08,319 --> 00:20:09,680
Playing chess against yourself,

311
00:20:11,079 --> 00:20:12,079
isn't it boring?

312
00:20:12,640 --> 00:20:14,839
One's ultimate opponent is oneself,

313
00:20:14,839 --> 00:20:16,240
all the way to the finish.

314
00:20:22,839 --> 00:20:25,039
Then, why introduce Yang Jinwan
to Rao Yuci?

315
00:20:29,799 --> 00:20:31,880
Why interfere in matters
you shouldn't interfere in?

316
00:20:33,400 --> 00:20:34,799
In a place like this,

317
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:35,799
drinking tea,

318
00:20:37,319 --> 00:20:39,880
playing chess, and having a quiet
and peaceful life,

319
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:41,400
isn't it good to enjoy yourself?

320
00:20:43,880 --> 00:20:45,160
The virtuous find much support.

321
00:20:45,880 --> 00:20:47,400
Even a child understands this.

322
00:20:47,480 --> 00:20:49,359
How can you not understand, Mr. Jiang?

323
00:20:50,800 --> 00:20:52,079
So you're going to help Rao Yuci

324
00:20:52,079 --> 00:20:53,559
all the way to the end, is that it?

325
00:20:54,400 --> 00:20:55,240
I have no choice.

326
00:20:55,720 --> 00:20:56,920
I just get along with her.

327
00:20:58,480 --> 00:21:00,440
Besides, Mr. Jiang,

328
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:01,799
in Chinese chess,

329
00:21:07,079 --> 00:21:08,359
(Generals)
the Generals never meet.

330
00:21:08,519 --> 00:21:09,519
Once they do,

331
00:21:09,720 --> 00:21:11,200
it's a final fight to the death.

332
00:21:15,319 --> 00:21:17,680
Since you still cling to our business,

333
00:21:20,359 --> 00:21:21,960
I'll make you lose once more.

334
00:21:23,759 --> 00:21:25,039
I'm getting old.

335
00:21:26,319 --> 00:21:28,039
I don't understand what you're saying.

336
00:21:28,039 --> 00:21:29,839
All I see is you talking nonsense.

337
00:21:35,400 --> 00:21:37,660
The fact you don't understand
isn't because you're old.

338
00:21:37,920 --> 00:21:39,039
Thinking that way

339
00:21:40,519 --> 00:21:42,079
is an insult to time itself.

340
00:21:44,599 --> 00:21:45,559
For all these years,

341
00:21:46,880 --> 00:21:50,440
you've been unwilling to admit
how your son really died, right?

342
00:21:54,079 --> 00:21:55,400
What do you mean by that?

343
00:21:58,559 --> 00:21:59,519
In 2014,

344
00:22:00,200 --> 00:22:02,519
everyone in the stock market
suffered a crushing defeat.

345
00:22:02,519 --> 00:22:03,599
Only you won.

346
00:22:05,400 --> 00:22:06,440
The stock that brought you

347
00:22:06,440 --> 00:22:07,279
the most profit

348
00:22:08,359 --> 00:22:09,720
was Virtual Pulse Tech.

349
00:22:09,759 --> 00:22:10,640
Do you remember?

350
00:22:13,839 --> 00:22:14,799
For all these years,

351
00:22:16,720 --> 00:22:17,759
you've always thought

352
00:22:18,960 --> 00:22:20,440
that I was the one who bought

353
00:22:20,759 --> 00:22:21,759
the shares you sold.

354
00:22:23,240 --> 00:22:24,599
But do you know

355
00:22:25,319 --> 00:22:26,359
who really took them?

356
00:22:32,119 --> 00:22:32,960
Wu Xiangnan.

357
00:22:32,960 --> 00:22:33,940
(Transferor: Jiang Dongchao.
Transferee: Wu Xiangnan)

358
00:22:36,559 --> 00:22:37,359
Yes.

359
00:22:39,519 --> 00:22:41,039
It was your late son,

360
00:22:42,000 --> 00:22:42,880
Wu Xiangnan.

361
00:22:43,880 --> 00:22:45,079
Jiang Dongchao, it was you.

362
00:22:46,200 --> 00:22:47,480
You're the one who set him up!

363
00:22:47,720 --> 00:22:48,880
You're the one who ruined him!

364
00:22:49,079 --> 00:22:50,279
How can you say that?

365
00:22:50,799 --> 00:22:51,720
If you hadn't ultimately

366
00:22:51,720 --> 00:22:52,920
turned your back on him,

367
00:22:52,920 --> 00:22:54,440
he wouldn't have chosen suicide.

368
00:22:57,319 --> 00:22:58,480
You won the stock market,

369
00:23:01,200 --> 00:23:02,400
but you lost your son.

370
00:23:03,960 --> 00:23:05,559
It seems you were right, Master.

371
00:23:07,440 --> 00:23:08,640
In the game of life,

372
00:23:09,039 --> 00:23:09,839
the opponent

373
00:23:13,400 --> 00:23:14,480
is always oneself.

374
00:23:19,319 --> 00:23:21,400
Jiang Dongchao, don't go.

375
00:23:21,640 --> 00:23:22,319
Jiang Dongchao!

376
00:23:22,319 --> 00:23:23,640
You can't leave!

377
00:23:28,680 --> 00:23:30,480
Jiang...

378
00:24:03,960 --> 00:24:05,640
We are Mr. Rabbit.

379
00:24:06,000 --> 00:24:07,240
We're here to help Duoduo.

380
00:24:08,519 --> 00:24:09,279
Don't go.

381
00:24:10,039 --> 00:24:11,359
Miss, we aren't scammers.

382
00:24:11,359 --> 00:24:12,559
We just want to help you.

383
00:24:12,839 --> 00:24:14,119
We are your friends.

384
00:24:14,200 --> 00:24:16,079
We really can help you.

385
00:24:16,680 --> 00:24:17,880
When destiny is changed,

386
00:24:18,480 --> 00:24:20,039
are you sure you're okay with it?

387
00:24:30,559 --> 00:24:32,079
(You once warned me)

388
00:24:33,319 --> 00:24:34,480
(that the things I do)

389
00:24:35,559 --> 00:24:36,920
(would also sweep up)

390
00:24:36,920 --> 00:24:38,160
(the people I care about.)

391
00:24:40,079 --> 00:24:40,960
(I didn't know)

392
00:24:42,640 --> 00:24:43,920
(that you'd be right.)

393
00:24:48,480 --> 00:24:50,440
Everyone has their own difficulties

394
00:24:50,440 --> 00:24:51,880
and shackles.

395
00:24:51,880 --> 00:24:53,240
They are very hard to unlock.

396
00:24:54,039 --> 00:24:55,480
After you are discharged this time,

397
00:24:55,480 --> 00:24:58,880
you will be facing a brand new world.

398
00:24:59,400 --> 00:25:01,240
It's different from the old one.

399
00:25:02,240 --> 00:25:02,960
Bai Liangliang

400
00:25:02,960 --> 00:25:05,039
is merely your simplest opponent.

401
00:25:05,799 --> 00:25:06,799
Not just you,

402
00:25:07,400 --> 00:25:09,400
everyone you care about

403
00:25:09,920 --> 00:25:12,119
will also be caught up in it.

404
00:25:21,599 --> 00:25:23,400
So, have your shackles been unlocked?

405
00:25:25,359 --> 00:25:26,799
What is your key?

406
00:25:33,599 --> 00:25:34,400
It's you.

407
00:25:39,200 --> 00:25:40,000
It's you.

408
00:25:42,599 --> 00:25:43,599
I wasn't able

409
00:25:43,599 --> 00:25:45,039
to help my own son.

410
00:25:47,400 --> 00:25:49,799
But helping you has given me hope.

411
00:25:50,720 --> 00:25:51,799
A father's hope

412
00:25:52,519 --> 00:25:54,519
of protecting his own child.

413
00:26:10,839 --> 00:26:11,640
Thank you.

414
00:26:13,200 --> 00:26:14,039
Thank you.

415
00:26:31,480 --> 00:26:32,559
I think I'm about

416
00:26:32,559 --> 00:26:33,960
to find my own key, too.

417
00:26:56,220 --> 00:26:58,980
(Rest in peace)

418
00:27:01,200 --> 00:27:02,000
Rao Yuci,

419
00:27:03,119 --> 00:27:04,240
what do you want?

420
00:27:06,359 --> 00:27:07,200
You know very well

421
00:27:07,200 --> 00:27:09,440
the real reason
Bai Muran committed suicide.

422
00:27:10,880 --> 00:27:13,200
Someone as selfish and cold as you

423
00:27:14,279 --> 00:27:15,599
will only push all the blame

424
00:27:16,680 --> 00:27:18,240
onto others.

425
00:27:18,720 --> 00:27:19,799
You can fool others,

426
00:27:19,799 --> 00:27:21,160
but can you fool yourself?

427
00:27:22,119 --> 00:27:23,799
The evil you sowed

428
00:27:24,759 --> 00:27:26,440
killed your own family.

429
00:27:28,920 --> 00:27:30,200
So, these four wreaths

430
00:27:32,160 --> 00:27:34,200
are a gift for your grandson
on your behalf.

431
00:27:36,200 --> 00:27:37,000
It seems the lesson

432
00:27:37,000 --> 00:27:38,119
he taught you wasn't enough.

433
00:27:38,200 --> 00:27:39,920
The lesson was not enough.

434
00:27:42,519 --> 00:27:43,319
Mr. Jiang,

435
00:27:44,920 --> 00:27:45,720
I know

436
00:27:46,500 --> 00:27:47,559
that no matter what I do,

437
00:27:47,920 --> 00:27:49,599
you'll never trust me again.

438
00:27:52,960 --> 00:27:54,500
Whether it's the tripartite cooperation

439
00:27:54,720 --> 00:27:56,039
or the financing conference,

440
00:27:56,599 --> 00:27:57,720
as long as I am here,

441
00:27:58,640 --> 00:28:00,039
you will not succeed.

442
00:28:01,880 --> 00:28:02,680
Rao Yuci,

443
00:28:03,079 --> 00:28:04,319
you are going to pay the price

444
00:28:04,319 --> 00:28:06,759
for everything you have done today.

445
00:28:06,759 --> 00:28:07,480
Fine.

446
00:28:08,599 --> 00:28:09,319
I'm someone

447
00:28:09,319 --> 00:28:10,680
from the underworld anyway.

448
00:28:11,759 --> 00:28:12,880
What do I have to fear?

449
00:28:14,039 --> 00:28:15,319
But you should remember,

450
00:28:16,839 --> 00:28:18,519
you will pay the price too.

451
00:28:39,119 --> 00:28:40,039
This world

452
00:28:40,079 --> 00:28:41,720
is full of drama.

453
00:28:44,240 --> 00:28:45,480
In less than a year,

454
00:28:46,519 --> 00:28:47,559
we

455
00:28:49,599 --> 00:28:52,079
have been dragged into the war
between you two young women.

456
00:28:55,039 --> 00:28:56,160
Li Qiang is dead.

457
00:28:56,960 --> 00:28:57,799
Muran is also...

458
00:29:00,519 --> 00:29:01,680
And then there's your mother.

459
00:29:05,440 --> 00:29:06,160
You've seen

460
00:29:06,160 --> 00:29:07,400
the current situation.

461
00:29:09,400 --> 00:29:10,519
The source of all this

462
00:29:10,519 --> 00:29:11,480
is just one person,

463
00:29:14,039 --> 00:29:14,880
Rao Yuci.

464
00:29:39,480 --> 00:29:41,759
A couple of days ago,

465
00:29:42,720 --> 00:29:43,519
I saw

466
00:29:43,519 --> 00:29:45,920
a ridiculous experiment on TV.

467
00:29:48,119 --> 00:29:51,640
It said they put a person

468
00:29:51,720 --> 00:29:55,480
on an instrument that precisely

469
00:29:55,519 --> 00:29:57,440
measures body weight.

470
00:29:58,440 --> 00:30:00,640
Then, they let him
fall into a deep sleep

471
00:30:03,039 --> 00:30:05,079
and suddenly woke him up.

472
00:30:07,440 --> 00:30:08,880
At the exact moment

473
00:30:08,880 --> 00:30:10,000
his soul left his body,

474
00:30:11,400 --> 00:30:13,440
the value on the instrument

475
00:30:13,640 --> 00:30:15,640
changed slightly.

476
00:30:16,079 --> 00:30:18,920
They said that
is the weight of the soul.

477
00:30:21,960 --> 00:30:23,200
So, take a guess.

478
00:30:23,279 --> 00:30:24,799
How much does a soul weigh?

479
00:30:30,160 --> 00:30:31,200
Twenty-one grams.

480
00:30:33,279 --> 00:30:34,319
A human soul

481
00:30:35,119 --> 00:30:37,279
is a mere twenty-one grams.

482
00:30:42,359 --> 00:30:46,319
After reading about this experiment,
I thought it was absolutely ridiculous.

483
00:30:46,319 --> 00:30:49,160
How could the human soul
possibly have a weight?

484
00:30:50,720 --> 00:30:52,359
Then, I understood.

485
00:30:55,039 --> 00:30:57,079
It is fear born from within.

486
00:30:57,920 --> 00:30:59,079
It is fear

487
00:30:59,759 --> 00:31:02,480
that gives the soul weight.

488
00:31:03,759 --> 00:31:05,079
The day Rao Yuci

489
00:31:05,079 --> 00:31:06,359
was beaten in the office,

490
00:31:08,000 --> 00:31:10,519
I could see fear filling

491
00:31:10,640 --> 00:31:12,279
Rao Yuci's eyes.

492
00:31:15,640 --> 00:31:18,519
And it was an inescapable fear.

493
00:31:27,480 --> 00:31:28,720
So, to take down Rao Yuci,

494
00:31:28,720 --> 00:31:30,359
the most important thing

495
00:31:30,359 --> 00:31:31,559
is to make her

496
00:31:31,559 --> 00:31:34,079
fear the world.

497
00:31:35,079 --> 00:31:36,880
You must make her feel

498
00:31:37,480 --> 00:31:39,359
the power of these twenty-one grams

499
00:31:39,359 --> 00:31:40,799
of fear constantly.

500
00:31:42,759 --> 00:31:44,039
And this fear

501
00:31:45,319 --> 00:31:46,519
comes from you.

502
00:31:48,200 --> 00:31:49,519
And it can only be you.

503
00:31:56,640 --> 00:31:57,440
So,

504
00:31:58,799 --> 00:32:01,039
you should know what to do now, right?

505
00:32:29,000 --> 00:32:30,640
Do you think she understood?

506
00:32:33,880 --> 00:32:34,880
She is smart.

507
00:32:36,359 --> 00:32:38,390
She knows how to exploit
an opponent's weaknesses.

508
00:32:53,720 --> 00:32:54,519
Miss Bai,

509
00:32:54,559 --> 00:32:56,799
these are the sleeping pills
for Mr. Xu as you requested.

510
00:32:59,039 --> 00:33:00,680
Mr. Xu hasn't been sleeping well lately,

511
00:33:00,960 --> 00:33:02,160
so medication is fine.

512
00:33:02,359 --> 00:33:04,000
But you must be careful with the dosage.

513
00:33:04,000 --> 00:33:06,190
Otherwise, it's easy to cause
dangerous hallucinations.

514
00:33:07,720 --> 00:33:08,519
Understood.

515
00:33:19,680 --> 00:33:20,480
Bai Xia.

516
00:33:24,480 --> 00:33:25,279
Bai Xia...

517
00:33:57,220 --> 00:33:58,620
(Bai Liangliang)

518
00:34:02,599 --> 00:34:03,400
Hello?

519
00:34:04,720 --> 00:34:05,640
Let's meet.

520
00:34:06,440 --> 00:34:07,440
It's not convenient.

521
00:34:11,880 --> 00:34:13,280
(Sima Yang's recording)
I found it on her computer.

522
00:34:13,559 --> 00:34:14,960
Ms. Bai, you'd better be careful.

523
00:34:15,320 --> 00:34:16,679
I want to join Investment Dept 1.

524
00:34:16,679 --> 00:34:18,340
(Sima Yang)

525
00:34:19,679 --> 00:34:21,719
I'll send you the address later.

526
00:34:43,559 --> 00:34:44,760
You still haven't made a move?

527
00:34:45,320 --> 00:34:46,840
How much longer are you going to wait?

528
00:34:47,280 --> 00:34:48,280
Don't worry, Grandmother.

529
00:34:49,000 --> 00:34:50,599
I'll take care of this.

530
00:35:10,199 --> 00:35:12,280
The next step depends on what you think,

531
00:35:13,079 --> 00:35:13,920
Sima Yang.

532
00:35:15,800 --> 00:35:16,840
Are you crazy?

533
00:35:18,159 --> 00:35:19,800
Are you trying
to make me commit a crime?

534
00:35:22,000 --> 00:35:23,079
I'm calling the police.

535
00:35:23,500 --> 00:35:25,270
I'm calling the police
to arrest you right now.

536
00:35:25,320 --> 00:35:26,360
Do you dare?

537
00:35:27,519 --> 00:35:28,639
Do you dare?

538
00:35:31,719 --> 00:35:32,519
Sima Yang,

539
00:35:33,159 --> 00:35:34,800
you and I are the same.

540
00:35:36,719 --> 00:35:37,800
You even completed

541
00:35:37,800 --> 00:35:39,679
your university studies
on financial aid.

542
00:35:40,880 --> 00:35:42,559
You fought tooth and nail

543
00:35:42,559 --> 00:35:43,719
just to get into Lysen.

544
00:35:43,719 --> 00:35:44,660
(110)

545
00:35:44,800 --> 00:35:47,119
A poor kid with no background

546
00:35:47,599 --> 00:35:48,960
who worked hard

547
00:35:49,239 --> 00:35:50,920
to get everything you have today.

548
00:35:52,400 --> 00:35:54,480
If it all vanished in an instant,

549
00:35:56,320 --> 00:35:57,599
could you accept that?

550
00:36:07,800 --> 00:36:09,880
If Rao Yuci leaves Lysen,

551
00:36:10,440 --> 00:36:11,519
is there anyone

552
00:36:11,719 --> 00:36:12,880
in Dept 3 more suited

553
00:36:12,880 --> 00:36:14,599
to lead this team than you?

554
00:36:17,760 --> 00:36:19,599
If you handle this well,

555
00:36:20,159 --> 00:36:21,239
Mr. Jiang

556
00:36:22,440 --> 00:36:23,920
will treat you well.

557
00:36:39,340 --> 00:36:43,060
=Episode 27=
(The Weight of the Soul)

558
00:36:43,580 --> 00:36:46,020
(All animals in this production
were treated humanely)

559
00:36:46,020 --> 00:36:52,220
♪Take a breath and swallow
the words you couldn't say♪

560
00:36:52,980 --> 00:36:56,180
♪No need to force your heart anymore♪

561
00:36:56,180 --> 00:37:00,700
♪Searching for the season
we once missed♪

562
00:37:00,700 --> 00:37:08,220
♪Leave this place,
though wounded still stay strong♪

563
00:37:08,220 --> 00:37:12,140
♪You must believe
one day the rain will fall♪

564
00:37:12,140 --> 00:37:16,180
♪And wash away the mud
that stains your soul♪

565
00:37:16,180 --> 00:37:19,700
♪Find your freedom in the wild♪

566
00:37:19,700 --> 00:37:23,660
♪Take your stride and move ahead♪

567
00:37:23,660 --> 00:37:27,820
♪I will stay behind
and wait for your eyes♪

568
00:37:27,820 --> 00:37:32,020
♪To rebuild
the same flesh and soul again♪

569
00:37:32,020 --> 00:37:35,820
♪Wander freely through the thorns♪

570
00:37:35,820 --> 00:37:39,900
♪Keep walking through the light♪

571
00:37:39,900 --> 00:37:44,100
♪Fate is absurd, don't stop for anyone♪

572
00:37:44,100 --> 00:37:50,420
♪What you dare to lose
will one day be your own♪

573
00:38:07,540 --> 00:38:14,180
♪I'm sorry, I still owe you these words♪

574
00:38:14,180 --> 00:38:18,020
♪An apology that came too late♪

575
00:38:18,020 --> 00:38:22,660
♪Yet it's also the path
that saves my soul♪

576
00:38:22,740 --> 00:38:30,140
♪When the cold wind
passes it takes the past away♪

577
00:38:30,140 --> 00:38:34,220
♪You must believe and stand unwavering♪

578
00:38:34,220 --> 00:38:38,300
♪There will be hands
to pull you from the deep♪

579
00:38:38,300 --> 00:38:42,300
♪Find your freedom in the silence♪

580
00:38:42,300 --> 00:38:46,060
♪Let your wounds be mended♪

581
00:38:46,060 --> 00:38:50,260
♪Gray is not the past
and pain is not a shame♪

582
00:38:50,260 --> 00:38:54,420
♪Sometimes the sunlight
makes the world look crueler♪

583
00:38:54,420 --> 00:38:58,140
♪Wander through the echoes of regret♪

584
00:38:58,140 --> 00:39:02,180
♪Be forgiven and be sheltered♪

585
00:39:02,180 --> 00:39:06,220
♪After everything shatters,
hold my hand♪

586
00:39:06,220 --> 00:39:12,420
♪A flower reborn
will finally bloom forever♪
